BOOLEAN BtJsr82Url::GetSecuritySettings (  BtSecuritySettings &  ses  )  const
 

Returns the specified security settings.

Parameters:
ses Reference to a variable to hold the security settings. When any security settings were specified they are mapped onto the values of the enumeration BtSecuritySettings and 'ses' is overwritten with the resulting value.
Returns:
'TRUE' when security settings were specified in the URL string the URL was constructed from, 'FALSE' otherwise. In the latter case, ses is left unchanged.
